# Local Qt 5 cross-build output. Produced by bin/rebuild_qt5_toolchain.sh
# (~1.5 GB of source + tarballs); without this entry, COPY . into the
# viewer image bloats by the same amount and yields a multi-GB image.
.qt5-toolchain-build
